Da je kriv ili nije kriv?

178
00:16:54,120 --> 00:16:55,850
Naravno, da je kriv.

179
00:16:55,850 --> 00:16:58,670
A ja sam mislio da mozemo
da pocnemo sa nasom porotom.

180
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:03,130
Naravno, glasamo da je kriv.

181
00:17:03,130 --> 00:17:04,980
Ja nisam shvatio..

182
00:17:08,870 --> 00:17:11,510
Spustite ruke, molim vas. Moja greska.

183
00:17:11,510 --> 00:17:14,530
Glasanje se ne racuna.
Oprostite ,molim vas.

184
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:24,170
Glasamo da vidimo ko
misli da je optuzeni kriv.

185
00:17:24,845 --> 00:17:28,288
Podignuta ruka znaci KRIV? Da.

186
00:17:28,910 --> 00:17:30,630
Samo hocu da budem siguran
da ne bi doslo do greske.

187
00:17:30,630 --> 00:17:34,740
Samo podigni ruku i nece biti greske. Da
li si ikada imao sastanak na poslu pre?

188
00:17:34,740 --> 00:17:36,300
Prestanite vec jednom.

189
00:17:37,636 --> 00:17:39,104
Sudija proleter.

190
00:17:39,930 --> 00:17:41,230
Glasajmo.

191
00:17:41,570 --> 00:17:45,660
Zasto mi glasamo da je
kriv? U cemu je razlika?

192
00:17:45,660 --> 00:17:46,620
Pa ne..

193
